					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Francesca Wade</h4>
												<p>Francesca Wade is the author of <em>Square Haunting: Five Writers in London Between the Wars</em> (2020). She has received fellowships from the Dorothy and Lewis B. Cullman Center, the Leon Levy Center for Biography and the Harvard Radcliffe Institute, and her writing has appeared in <em>The New York Review of Books</em>, <em>London Review of Books</em>, <em>Paris Review</em>, <em>Granta</em>, and elsewhere.</p>
